  <title translate="true">Filter</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Filter</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Header 2" style="text-align:right;"><link displaytype="image" src="New_Back_Arrow_icon.gif" type="topiclink" href="Curriculum"></link><text styleclass="Header 2" style="font-size:8pt;" translate="true"> </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Curriculum" styleclass="Answer" style="font-size:8pt;" translate="true">Return to Curriculum Menu</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Header 2" style="text-align:left; text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><image src="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Answer" style="font-size:8pt;"></image><tab/><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_plus1.gif" styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[What is a Standards Filter?]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Header 2" style="text-align:left; text-indent:-18px; margin-left:42px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">A Standards Filter is a pre determined list of standards that a user can create to make free form Assessment construction much faster.  A Standards Filter is unique to every user and will &quot;stick&quot; with a user until deleted.  After building a Standards Filter the user will have access to their filter through the Standard Filter option under the Standard Search Options on an assessment.  When Standard Filter is chosen the standards from the filter will display as choices for each question allowing the user to have a much shorter list to choose standards from for the assessment.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><image src="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;"></image><tab/><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_plus1.gif" styleclass="Font Style" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none; text-transform:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000; background-color:transparent; letter-spacing:normal; letter-scaling:100%;"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[How do I build a Standard filter?]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:42px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">In order to build a standards filter please follow the directions below:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"></para>
          <list id="21" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000080;">
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Curriculum</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Filter</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Select the criteria for the standard(s) you would like in your filter</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Find</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Standards</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Select the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">check</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">boxes</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> under  the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Sel</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> column next to the desired standards</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Update</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Filter</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Answer"></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">To remove standards from the filter:</text></para>
          <list id="22" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="%0:s." format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; color:#000080;">
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Uncheck</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> the box next to the standard to be removed</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Update</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Filter</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:0px;"><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic; text-decoration:none;" translate="true">A standard filter can be updated or deleted at any time.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"></para>
  </body>
